               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction
 - Maqdǝma Wangel “Introduction to the Gospels”
                     (fols. 5ra-9rb) [including: the “Synopsis of Classes” (fols. 9rb-9vb), On the
                     72 disciples (fols. 9vb-9vc), On the Episcopal Sees (fol. 9vc), Letter of
                     Eusebius to Carpianus (fols. 9vc-10rc)]
 - Canon tables (fols.
                     10v-11v)
 - On the Reliability of the Gospels (fols. 12ra-12rb)
 II)
                     Gospel of Matthew (fols. 12rb-60va)
 - Biography of Matthew (fols.
                     12rb-12rc)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew – 69 titles
                     (fol. 12rc-12vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Mātewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 13ra-60rb)
                     
 - Postscript (fols. 60va)
 III) Gospel of Mark (fols.60vb-87rb)
                     - Biography of Mark (fols. 60vb-61rb)
 - List of the “tituli” for the
                     Gospel of Mark – 48 titles (fols. 61rb-61vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Mārqos “Gospel of
                     Mark” (fols. 63ra-87rb)
 - Postscript (fols. 87rb)
 IV) Gospel of Luke
                     (fols. 87rb-133vb)
 - Biography of Luke (fols. 87rb-87vb)
 - Bǝsrāta
                     Luqās “Gospel of Luke” (fols. 89ra-133ra)
 - Postscript (fol. 133ra) 
                     - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke – 84 titles (fols.
                     133rb-133vb)
 V) Gospel of John (fols.134ra)
 - Biography of John (fol.
                     134ra-134vb)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John – 19 titles
                     (fol. 134vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols. 135ra-170va)
                     - Postscript (fols. 170va-170vb).</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

